unittitle_ssm: Tamiment Library and Robert F. Wagner Labor Archives Collection of Religion Serials
abstract_ssm: The Tamiment Library and Robert F. Wagner Labor Archives Collection of Religion Serials contains over 90 titles published in the United States, Israel, Canada, and Europe on religious issues throughout the world between 1919 and 1999.  The bulk of the collection consists of serials published between the 1940s and the 1990s by Jewish organizations in the United States.
